TLDR: This paper proposes SPACERTC, a satellite-cloud cooperative framework that adaptively selects relay servers upon satellites and cloud sites to build an overlay network which enables diverse close-to-optimal paths, and then judiciously allocates RTC flows upon the network to facilitate low-latency interactions.},
	keywords = {Prototypes, Satellites, Real-time systems, Cloud computing, Quality of experience, Teleconferencing, Web and internet services},
	pages = {1339--1348},
