影响因子: 4.7
5年影响因子: 4.6
EI: 是
CCF: C},
	keywords = {Security, Switches, Delays, security, Middleboxes, Computer crime, Denial-of-service attack, Memory management, prototype implementation, Software-defined networks, testbed experimentation},
	pages = {3121--3139},
	file = {IEEE Xplore Abstract Record:/Users/kc/Zotero/storage/ZH93JY98/9311137.html:text/html;Ilha 等 - 2021 - Euclid A Fully In-Network, P4-Based Approach for Real-Time DDoS Attack Detection and Mitigation.pdf:/Users/kc/Zotero/storage/KYH4H9BW/Ilha 等 - 2021 - Euclid A Fully In-Network, P4-Based Approach for Real-Time DDoS Attack Detection and Mitigation.pdf:application/pdf},
